commits.message: feat(query): Lazy.followPath true streaming and explain selectivity with stages
merge: feat/query-warnings  main (query warnings, deprecate where(predicate), auto-compact test fix)
test(query): add/port unit tests to temp workspace; global cleanup for tmp-*.synapsedb
docs: API appendix for lazy/streaming/explain; update tutorials and test guide
refactor: remove Gremlin and GraphQL query engines
chore(lint): fix require-await/no-any/no-this-alias; format plan nodes; stabilize explain estimate types
fix: stabilize plugin rollout and satisfy lint
ci: assert no tmp-*.synapsedb leftovers after build
merge: feat/qb-lazy-exec  main (LazyQueryBuilder + findLazy, lazy union, docs updates)
